text: Mulla-Kamysh () is a rural locality (a village) in Verkhnebishindinsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 40 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Tuymazy, 4 km from Verkhniye Bishindy. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Mulla-Kamysh
